high_descs: Turn left and walk to the green table then take a step to your right so you clear the green table then take a step forward then turn left.
Pick up the egg that's in front of you that's underneath the sponge.
Turn around and walk to the sink then take a step to your left.
Wash the egg in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn around to face the table.
Put the egg under the middle tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean egg on the table.

high_descs: Pick up an egg from the table
Wash the egg in the sink
Place the egg back on the table
anns.task_desc: Wash an egg and place it back on a table

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the other side of the island to face the red vegetables.
Pick up the egg from the counter behind the apple.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Place the egg in the sink, rinse off the egg, take the egg out of the sink.
Turn around and face the counter.
Place the egg on the counter in front of the apple.
anns.task_desc: To rinse off an egg and place it on the table.
